        {
            "id": 6097600,
            "title": "盤中速報 - Applovin Corp - Class A(APP-US)大漲5.23%，報410.99美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Applovin Corp - Class A(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:APP:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/APP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">APP-US</a>)截至台北時間07日21:50股價上漲20.42美元，報410.99美元，漲幅5.23%，成交量3,838,276（股），盤中最高價411.40美元、最低價385.10美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.28%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.48%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.87%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+2.44%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>Applovin Corp - Class A(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:APP:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/APP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">APP-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+7.5%</li> <li>近 1 月：+14.32%</li> <li>近 3 月：+28.22%</li> <li>近 6 月：+2.61%</li> <li>今年以來：+20.61%</li></ul></section></main>",
